  "name": "PromptPanel",
  "description": "Open-source native macOS prompt manager and snippet launcher for AI power users. PromptPanel is a ChatGPT prompt manager, Claude prompt library, Cursor snippet manager, and local-first prompt library that stores reusable prompts locally in SQLite and uses a global hotkey panel to paste them into ChatGPT, Claude, Cursor, Copilot, VS Code, Terminal, browsers, or any text field.",
